ead></head><body>\n<ul>\n<li>Air Hockey Classic - <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ignacemaes.airhockey\">Android</a>, <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/air-hockey-classic/id1535374629\">iOS</a> - Play the classic 'Air Hockey' arcade game now on your mobile device! By <a href=\"https://ignacemaes.com/\">Ignace Maes</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"board\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#board\" aria-label=\"board permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Board</h4>\n<!--lint ignore double-link--><html><head></head><body>\n<ul>\n<li>Four In A Row - <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ignacemaes.fourinarow\">Android</a>, <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/four-in-a-row-classic/id1495540053\">iOS</a> - Play the classic 'Four In A Row' board game! Will you be the first to connect 4 of your chips? Challenge the AI, or play against your friends and family. By <a href=\"https://ignacemaes.com/\">Ignace Maes</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"casual-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#casual-1\" aria-label=\"casual 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Casual</h4>\n<!--lint ignore double-link--><html><head></head><body>\n<ul>\n<li>KINGA - <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.knoeyes.games.kinga\">Android</a>, <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/kinga/id1506422810\">iOS</a> - Protect the cookie from the pesky flies. By <a href=\"https://kevinomyonga.com\">Kevin Omyonga</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!--lint ignore double-link--><html><head></head><body>\n<ul>\n<li>Dhoruba - <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.knoeyes.games.dhoruba\">Android</a>, <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/ke/app/dhoruba/id1542324108\">iOS</a> - Can You Stand The Rain? By <a href=\"https://kevinomyonga.com\">Kevin Omyonga</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!--lint ignore double-link--><html><head></head><body>\n<ul>\n<li>Wormo - <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tbuonomo.wormo\">Android</a>, <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/wormo-the-game/id1530797595\">iOS</a> - Meet Wormo the gooey worm in this wonderful casual game! Think you can put wormo in the nest? Think again, it requires an extraordinary technique.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>By Tommy Buonomo (<a href=\"https://frenchiegames.app/#/\">Frenchie Games</a>)</p>\n<h4 id=\"metroidvania\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#metroidvania\" aria-label=\"metroidvania permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Metroidvania</h4>\n<!--lint ignore double-link--><html><head></head><body>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://fireslime.xyz/games/tales.html\">Tales of a Lost Mine</a> - <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=xyz.fireslime.tales&#x26;pcampaignid=MKT-Other-global-all-co-prtnr-py-PartBadge-Mar2515-1\">Android</a> - An awesome platform-adventure Metroidvania. Get in the role of a brave explorer and uncover the secrets of a long lost time. By <a href=\"https://fireslime.xyz\">FireSlime</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"puzzle-games\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#puzzle-games\" aria-label=\"puzzle games permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Puzzle Games</h4>\n<!--lint ignore double-link--><html><head></head><body>\n<ul>\n<li>Ripple Effect Puzzle - <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tbuonomo.rippleeffectpuzzle\">Android</a>, <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id1521454937\">iOS</a> - A sophisticated variation of Sudoku.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>By Tommy Buonomo (<a href=\"https://frenchiegames.app/#/\">Frenchie Games</a>)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tile Paths - <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.naslausky.tile_paths\">Android</a> - Drag the tiles and find the best path to make your character collect all items while avoiding the enemy. With 10 different stages you can challenge your friends to see who gets the best highscore in every one of them. By <a href=\"https://github.com/naslausky\">Naslausky</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"sports\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sports\" aria-label=\