ore extreme and longer races. Keep going and win the ultimate world tour! By <a href=\"https://github.com/ikbendewilliam\">ikbendewilliam</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"tower-defense\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tower-defense\" aria-label=\"tower defense permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tower Defense</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Xtrike - <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=online.xtrike.xtrike\">Android</a> - An awesome strategic tower defense game. Build your battle units and destroy enemies. By <a href=\"http://www.xtrike.online/\">White Wood City</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"non-english-content\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#non-english-content\" aria-label=\"non english content permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Non-English Content</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/flame-engine/awesome-flame/blob/main/CONTENT_ZH.md\">Mandarin Chinese (中文)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"contributing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contributing\" aria-label=\"